{
  "stem": "10710.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were 100 people-- were, were living in three villas in the outside or outskirts of the town.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they make us come every morning to work on that-- in that school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The first day we came, they shaved our heads completely.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We-- and, and they told us whoever cannot work, who was sick, who was old, who was too young to work, they should come out of the-- of the line and report.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Of course, nobody wanted to go, because they knew what's going to be-- it was a very bad camp.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I remember the first day, we were working in the-- what, what our job was to do is to make a [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This is how they should teach them how to shoot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a big walk-- it was a big mountain, and we had to straighten out the mountain like this.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they should-- they make all kinds of preparations to make-- they should be able to teach them how to shoot.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But the conditions in Rabka was very bad.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "There was one man, the, the commandant from the camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "His name was Rosen-- Wilhelm Rosenbaum.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was a sadist.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I have never seen anybody like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He, he was walking around with a-- with a [INAUDIBLE], with the-- you know, from leather what you--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A whip, right.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "On the end of the whip, he had a metal thing.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was hitting from the back, it came under your eye.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So most of the people had black eyes from [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And women, he was merciless.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he found anybody, a Jew with the name Rosenbaum, he, he shot the whole family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was going around with a gun.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was going around-- if somebody did something wrong, he put his name down.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
